What if we told you it only takes 30 seconds to make a sexy summer cocktail? And all you need is 2 ingredients:

1. Your fav spirit from the McDowell’s X Series
2. A Jimmy’s Cocktail to match! 

Whether you’re team vodka, gin, or rum - each spirit pairs SO BEAUTIFULLY a bottle of Jimmy’s Cocktail—Green Apple Martini, Sparkling Tonic Water, or Popstar Martini—and you’re ready to impress with no effort needed!

Just:
Ice it, Spike it, Mix it, Sip it.
And yes, it slurpssss!

This summer, Jimmy’s is your party go-to cause each cocktail is just tastier than the last and it’s such an easy summer fix! 
2 bottles, endless possibilities!
